{"tid":1156804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"刀賊劫ok便利店 職員匿貨倉保不失","createTime":"2019-05-16T00:08:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T07:16:22.000Z","uid":3090,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"878ec13a5714eea12c6a93aee9aba2342f58805c","tid":1156804,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T00:08:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pu4tniT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpu4tniT.png&h=d2c1121e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RVD2rLz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRVD2rLz.png&h=f3c00de6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新蒲崗寧遠街10至20號地下ok便利店，凌晨2時53分，一名戴口罩賊人闖入店內，從膠袋取出一把約1呎半長牛肉刀，指嚇櫃枱姓邱61歲女職員，聲稱打劫，女職員受驚衝入櫃枱旁的貨倉躲避。<br />\n<br />\n其時貨倉亦有一名男職員，兩人將門鎖上，以及報警求助。賊人事敗逃去。警方到場在附近兜截沒有發現，翻查錄影帶追緝賊人歸案。<br />\n<br />\n賊人年約30至40歲，身高約1.7米，蓄金及啡短髮，戴口罩及眼鏡，案發時身穿黑色外套，白色上衣。"},{"pid":"587c0bf44b3e2b4b7a4caba66eaf95f17eb83a22","tid":1156804,"uid":223256,"like":54,"dislike":2,"score":52,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T00:13:20.000Z","msg":"職員唔見左<br />\n個賊唔識自己開錢箱囉錢?<br />\n囉唔到錢<br />\n都偷d貴貨啦<br />\n正笨賊<br />\n書都唔讀學人做賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a53a93d52ab5c93fe255a8c280bfbdcfd83ca2b","tid":1156804,"uid":65346,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T00:16:08.000Z","msg":"打劫忌多口,同埋多同鈍器,打暈最好 !"},{"pid":"07df09c2b3c5f20e0f4fe4014c11c37313113c4e","tid":1156804,"uid":230965,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"587c0bf44b3e2b4b7a4caba66eaf95f17eb83a22","tid":1156804,"uid":223256,"like":54,"dislike":2,"score":52,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T00:13:20.000Z","msg":"職員唔見左<br />\n個賊唔識自己開錢箱囉錢?<br />\n囉唔到錢<br />\n都偷d貴貨啦<br />\n正笨賊<br />\n書都唔讀學人做賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T00:16:52.000Z","msg":"教做賊嗰堂訓左覺"},{"pid":"2fe02d2188ac38c0cc84d1a13a4fd24038b7bd81","tid":1156804,"uid":78666,"like":0,"d